column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE CARAMEL, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210993793
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, glucose syrup, cocoa butter, glucose-fructose syrup, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa mass, whey powder (from MILK), emulsifiers (E 442, E 471, E 476, sunflower lecithin), salt, sodium bicarbonate, flavourings. Family milk chocolate: Milk solids 20% minimum, Actual 23%. Cocoa solids 20% minimum.Contains vegetable fats in addition to cocoa butter.**The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of family milk chocolate. MAY CONTAIN NUTS. Date available: 01/19/2018 Date last updated by company: 01/19/2018
